Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:10.00,Notes,,0,0,0,,字幕搬運：大風鈴               來自極影字幕組、bilibili\N業餘謄抄，僅供交流學習
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.30,0:00:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1104,697.8)}去千葉那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.30,0:00:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1116,616.2)}我可能要搬家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.30,0:00:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1044,249)}有件事必須告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.30,0:00:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1430.4,357)}唉？什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.90,0:00:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,小太郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  你要搬家嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.07,0:00:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼時候？要搬去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我還在查那邊的高中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.47,0:00:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道光明高中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.37,0:01:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思  那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:29.77,OPJP,,0,0,0,,なんとなく頭の中で君が  離れなくなっていたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:29.77,OPCN,,0,0,0,,不知為何  你的身影一直縈繞在我的腦海
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:50.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,途切れの会話だね いつも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:50.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,我們倆的對話總是斷斷續續呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:58.13,OPJP,,0,0,0,,息も吐き出せないほどのことを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:58.13,OPCN,,0,0,0,,和你交談時  我總覺得呼吸困難
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:02:01.35,OPJP,,0,0,0,,目が合った瞬間に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:02:01.35,OPCN,,0,0,0,,在眼神交會的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:11.19,OPJP,,0,0,0,,また何かが胸を貫いてゆく  今!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:11.19,OPCN,,0,0,0,,我感覺彷彿有什麼擊中了我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:18.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,,大好きな人がイマココに居る、居るんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:18.40,OPCN,,0,0,0,,現在我最喜歡的人就在我眼前  在我眼前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:25.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,最高の毎日は恋の晴れパレーパレード
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:25.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,,每天都幸福得像戀愛大遊行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:32.13,OPJP,,0,0,0,,近づきたい 誰よりも君に今、いま以上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:32.13,OPCN,,0,0,0,,我想靠近你  我想靠得比誰都近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:42.68,OPJP,,0,0,0,,会いたくて会いに行く  笑顔また見つけに行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:42.68,OPCN,,0,0,0,,我想見你  我現在就去尋找你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.63,0:02:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,平時表現分也夠  應該沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣啊  我放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.00,0:03:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真是辛苦啊  是父親的工作原因嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  畢竟關鍵時期  我還擔心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.27,0:03:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這是申請表
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嚇我一跳  突然來那麼個消息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我想讓你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.07,0:03:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的三方面談
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,決定接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.85,0:04:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,光明高中的推薦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,因為離得遠了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是小茜的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就算離得遠也沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我要不要也考那裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,推薦肯定拿不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,參加常規考試
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然遠的要死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.75,0:04:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好像要花兩個小時以上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我決定上那家補習班了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,週六就是川越祭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.95,0:05:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我會去看的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,啊    嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.72,0:05:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.79,0:06:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,一二一二……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.35,0:06:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  大家都在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,關係真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的  太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.57,0:06:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,準備？剪刀石頭布
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哇  贏了耶  小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-什麼鬼啊  該死  -偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,吶  大家一起去鬼屋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.82,0:07:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好像很好玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,騙小孩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？你怕了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,激我也沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-你這才厲害吧  -厲害？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那個  小太郎那裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？剛才那是安曇？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,欸  挺帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,發揮挺不錯的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,一般吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,真苛刻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你上次說的  輕小說的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:08:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,保持原樣不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.42,0:09:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,之前給我讀的小說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得  給喜歡輕小說的人看也沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,喲  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.85,0:09:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,距離下次換人還有段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,去逛逛祭奠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.05,0:09:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,晚些見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,去逛逛唄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1180.8,541.8)}我現在有點空了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1413.6,652.2)}在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(741.6,899.4)}門前橫丁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1173.6,993)}跟田徑部的人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1276.8,285)}跟田徑部的人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(866.4,678.6)}到附近了聯繫你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1322.4,805.8)}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好  開始囉  丟垃圾猜拳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,剪刀石頭布
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好久沒吃薯戀了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好想吃薯戀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,還吃得下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  當然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,都沒練田徑了  吃這麼多不妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,吶  水野
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.27,0:10:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,去買薯戀嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.97,0:10:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這就吃上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,吃的真幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.37,0:10:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我超愛吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.77,0:10:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟是川越的名產
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.53,0:10:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,搬走就吃不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:10:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要說這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.82,0:11:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我好像有點不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說你要搬家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡你很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你努力奔跑的樣子  我一直看著的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那個……我有男朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.45,0:11:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.37,0:12:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.35,0:12:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.97,0:12:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼是安曇啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我絕對比他了解水野
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我從一開始就一直……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,一直最喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起  我……當比良是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然你也很重要……但不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.30,0:12:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想好好的說出來過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1099.2,352.2)}到附近了聯繫你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1449.6,532.2)}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(808.8,606.6)}來時鐘這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為見不了面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我來的時候跟大家說先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你剛剛跟比良在一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.05,0:13:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,就你們兩個？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,丟垃圾猜拳輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.67,0:13:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.80,0:13:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我看了小太郎跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,太精彩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,休息到什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,一小時左右
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,很快就要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,吃薯戀好了  小茜要嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  小太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,啊嘞  小太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.76,0:14:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是小太郎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你有女朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你管我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.15,0:14:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你這話說的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你們誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.39,0:14:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真是青春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會告訴你老爸的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,瞎說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,走了 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.07,0:14:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,安曇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我感覺你跟平時不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,生氣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.90,0:14:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,才沒有生氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就是生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是搬家的事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,可只有這件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.07,0:14:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,別管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.55,0:14:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,吶  說清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:15:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好不容易一次的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我很生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.35,0:15:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,單獨和別的男生一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,倒也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.07,0:15:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那個……剛剛被告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我去給你買茶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,都沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我得走了  拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1243.2,114.6)}來時鐘這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(760.8,263.4)}嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(696,405)}稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(547.2,114.6)}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(909.6,232.2)}有件事必須告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1346.4,429)}欸？什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(859.2,589.8)}我可能要搬家  去千葉那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.10,0:18:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天也睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.70,0:18:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,正準備學習就睏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.52,0:18:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,真心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,正準備發完LINE就學習的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,父母就說趕快去學習
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,說得我都沒動力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.67,0:18:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真心難受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣意思就變了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡需要多注意點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.45,0:19:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那個  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會有這本的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  有人想報
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.25,0:20:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這個  老師說有人想報
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.22,0:20:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是小太郎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:43.76,INJP,,0,0,0,,いつもそう単純で
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:43.76,INCN,,0,0,0,,一次又一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.60,0:20:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我要考啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,連父母都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:49.68,INJP,,0,0,0,,クダラナイことがきっかけで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:49.68,INCN,,0,0,0,,起因是如此無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,估計會反對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:55.69,INJP,,0,0,0,,傷つけてしまうよね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:55.69,INCN,,0,0,0,,為何總因瑣事受傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不過  我會說服他們的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:21:02.53,INJP,,0,0,0,,途切れてく会話虚しいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:21:02.53,INCN,,0,0,0,,戛然而止的對話  好空虛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我打算先跟父母談完再告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.02,0:21:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,將來的計劃  還有小說的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:08.66,INJP,,0,0,0,,言葉が不器用すぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:08.66,INCN,,0,0,0,,總是不善言表
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:13.62,INJP,,0,0,0,,邪魔ばかりする
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:13.62,INCN,,0,0,0,,障礙一直不斷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.77,0:21:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我考慮了很久才決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:20.55,INJP,,0,0,0,,好きなのに伝わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:20.55,INCN,,0,0,0,,連喜歡都說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我想一直跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.65,0:21:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.55,0:21:29.56,INJP,,0,0,0,,こんな想い切なくて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.55,0:21:29.56,INCN,,0,0,0,,這份思念好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.56,0:21:32.98,INJP,,0,0,0,,「愛しい」だなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.56,0:21:32.98,INCN,,0,0,0,,雖然還
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:35.94,INJP,,0,0,0,,言い慣れてないケド
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:35.94,INCN,,0,0,0,,不習慣表達眷念
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:42.28,INJP,,0,0,0,,今なら言えるよ君のために
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:42.28,INCN,,0,0,0,,現在一定能說出口  為了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,上次那件事  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:48.24,INJP,,0,0,0,,となりで笑っていてくれるのならば
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:48.24,INCN,,0,0,0,,只要你微笑著陪在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.42,0:21:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,沒告訴你……
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為你再也不理我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:54.33,INJP,,0,0,0,,これ以上他に何も要らないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:54.33,INCN,,0,0,0,,我別無他求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,才沒這回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:22:00.59,INJP,,0,0,0,,出逢えたことから全ては始まった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:22:00.59,INCN,,0,0,0,,相遇那一刻一切都開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:06.72,INJP,,0,0,0,,傷つけあう日もあるけれども
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:06.72,INCN,,0,0,0,,雖然也有互相傷害的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:12.85,INJP,,0,0,0,,「いっしょにいたい」とそう思えることが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:12.85,INCN,,0,0,0,,「想和你在一起的念頭」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.85,0:22:22.82,INJP,,0,0,0,,まだ知らない明日へと つながってゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.85,0:22:22.82,INCN,,0,0,0,,必將連接未知的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.06,0:22:40.54,EDJP,,0,0,0,,夕暮れ落ちる前に白い月が昇る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.06,0:22:40.54,EDCN,,0,0,0,,夜幕還未完全降臨 潔白的月光便灑落大地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.58,0:22:46.88,EDJP,,0,0,0,,春風優しく2つの影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.58,0:22:46.88,EDCN,,0,0,0,,春風溫柔地拂過二人的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:53.43,EDJP,,0,0,0,,ささやくように包んでいたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:53.43,EDCN,,0,0,0,,靜悄悄地圍繞在你我身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.43,0:23:06.56,EDJP,,0,0,0,,初めてこんなに誰かを想った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.43,0:23:06.56,EDCN,,0,0,0,,第一次發現在腦海中 有著一個身影揮之不去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.56,0:23:12.32,EDJP,,0,0,0,,いつもどうしていいのかわからなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.56,0:23:12.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,,總是一直不知道該如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.32,0:23:18.92,EDJP,,0,0,0,,君への想いはこぼれるほどあるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.32,0:23:18.92,EDCN,,0,0,0,,明明對你的思念早已溢滿心田
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.92,0:23:26.38,EDJP,,0,0,0,,つないだ右手もぎこちないキスも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.92,0:23:26.38,EDCN,,0,0,0,,緊緊握住的右手也好 笨拙生疏的接吻也好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:32.96,EDJP,,0,0,0,,それだけがこの世界の全てだった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:32.96,EDCN,,0,0,0,,僅僅只是這些 卻已然成為了我世界的一切的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.96,0:23:39.81,EDJP,,0,0,0,,今日も君からもらった言葉を抱きしめている
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.96,0:23:39.81,EDCN,,0,0,0,,今天又一次將你的言語擁入心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.81,0:23:45.90,EDJP,,0,0,0,,私にとってそれはまるで月明かり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.81,0:23:45.90,EDCN,,0,0,0,,因那對於我而言宛若月明之光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.90,0:23:56.64,EDJP,,0,0,0,,二人で見上げたあの時みたいにきれい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.90,0:23:56.64,EDCN,,0,0,0,,正如我們那天一起仰望的 那般美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.25,0:24:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,文藝部  集合
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.22,0:24:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,要拍畢業照囉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.95,0:24:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,有這麼多幽靈部員
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.97,0:24:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？文藝部？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.85,0:24:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.10,0:24:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,欸  沒……
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.17,0:24:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不知道……
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.66,0:24:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好  要拍囉
